title: Week 8 Preview & New Top 25 Draft Prospects List
itunes:title: Week 8 Preview & New Top 25 Draft Prospects List
description:
DJ & Bucky preview all of the Week 8 NFL matchups (1:10). They also break down their latest Top 25 Draft Prospects List from the 2018 college football season (16:25) including why Duke QB Daniel Jones is a sleeper candidate (17:15). To close the show, the guys preview the biggest games on the Week 9 college football slate (27:05).
